{"id": 2896, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常生活里有哪些极易引发你纠结的小事？", "description": "触发你“左右为难”技能的小事件。（图片来源：istock ©️ Malombra76 ）", "record_count": 3799, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190411180016xy6ZhMRS5A7Gj29a.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-16T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 339456, "content": "要不要早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544181}, {"id": 339968, "content": "起床还是不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378845}, {"id": 339457, "content": "相中两件衣服，买哪件？😜", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638450}, {"id": 339713, "content": "每次考试ABCD排除了A和B，到底是选C还是选D？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639103}, {"id": 339458, "content": "发现现有的回答我全占了", "image": "img/option/option/2019041612374324YwW9MpdJgovkZh.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038439}, {"id": 339459, "content": "吃什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630629}, {"id": 338692, "content": "宿舍舍友还没起而你早醒了，你是起床还是在床上玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339460, "content": "怎么复习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630629}, {"id": 343812, "content": "今天吃什么，出门穿什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1508716}, {"id": 338693, "content": "买东西第二件半价／多买满减优惠时到底要不要多买点", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339461, "content": "买这件还是那件？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633105}, {"id": 338694, "content": "你刚到站台地铁响了快关门了要不要跑着试试冲上去", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339462, "content": "考试选ABCD", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1636837}, {"id": 338695, "content": "走在前面的人肩并肩把路挡住，到底要不要超过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339463, "content": "高跟鞋到底买大一码还是刚刚好？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418526}, {"id": 339464, "content": "买还是不买？That‘s a question！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 515073}, {"id": 339465, "content": "送礼物还是送礼金", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635123}, {"id": 339466, "content": "是先写还是先背", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568690}, {"id": 339978, "content": "纠结要不要点开对话框和朋友聊天，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639563}, {"id": 339467, "content": "买什么衣服\n买什么手机\n买什么鞋子\n连买书包都纠结\n我的纠结根源是穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310125}, {"id": 340491, "content": "这么多作业先做哪一个好呢……算了，刷会好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 339468, "content": "这道题选b还是a 感觉都对啊 然而正确大案是c🤷‍♂️", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602104}, {"id": 339981, "content": "到底要涂哪个口红", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074643}, {"id": 339470, "content": "冬天太冷究竟是躺下被窝里还是起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632143}, {"id": 339471, "content": "明天吃什么🤔\n每天晚上开始准备第二天便当的我思考这个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629519}, {"id": 340239, "content": "学还是不学这是一个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640906}, {"id": 339473, "content": "买了酸奶 该喝那个", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637241}, {"id": 339474, "content": "今天去几食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635604}, {"id": 339475, "content": "三分化还是五分化\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639272}, {"id": 339476, "content": "今天还有什么事没做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634995}, {"id": 339477, "content": "明天穿什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634783}, {"id": 339478, "content": "遇到同学说同学偷东西的时候，不知道怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639287}, {"id": 339479, "content": "无聊干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 339480, "content": "还有时间睡，要不要起床？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 339481, "content": "吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632611}, {"id": 340250, "content": "吃不吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623602}, {"id": 339483, "content": "思修课是玩手机还是看其他书", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 339739, "content": "大风天，头发又乱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451145}, {"id": 339485, "content": "要不要去健身房啊\n今天看哪本书啊\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639317}, {"id": 339486, "content": "去食堂吃啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456839}, {"id": 339487, "content": "记笔记还是等待幻灯片", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604070}, {"id": 339488, "content": "今天穿什么", "image": "img/option/option/20190416143220ofaHVbSnhWR3wFg9.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639095}, {"id": 339489, "content": "闹钟隔几分钟定一个？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639323}, {"id": 339490, "content": "嘴巴贪吃，内心抗拒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638870}, {"id": 339746, "content": "吃完饭的碗要不要今天洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "p